author: Epictetus
message: Practice yourself, for heavens sake in little things, and then proceed to greater.
title: Thought of the day

author: Seneca
message: If one does not know to which port is sailing, no wind is favorable.
title: Thought of the day

message: Our greatest glory is not in never failing but rising everytime we fall.
title: Thought of the day

message: Being right is highly overrated. Even a stopped clock is right twice a day.
title: Thought of the day
